query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(k mk mi_idx) */ select min(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
min(t.title) AS north_european_dark_production
from keyword AS k
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IS NOT NULL AND k.keyword IN ('sequel',
'tv-special',
'marvel-comics',
'time-in-title')
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.info < '6.3'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2002
inner join info_type AS it2
on it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating'
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('German',
'Bulgaria',
'American',
'Swedish',
'Norway',
'Sweden',
'USA',
'America',
'Germany',
'Canada')
inner join info_type AS it1
on it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries'
inner join kind_type AS kt
on kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('video movie',
'episode');
